http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Thiruvananthapuram/VS-objects-to-move-to-open-annexe/article13995233.ece

: Leader of the Opposition V.S. Achuthanandan has asked the government not to inaugurate the seven-storeyed secretariat annexe building without obtaining certification from the Fire and Rescue Services.In a statement here on Monday, Mr. Achuthanandan said opening the annexe building without the Fire and Rescue Service’s certificate would only help the apartment mafia, which would cite it as an instance to commission their projects without certificate from the Fire and Rescue Services.‘Illegal move’The government move was illegal and dangerous, the Leader of the Opposition.